title: 40 MIN KILLER HIIT WORKOUT - Full Body, No Equipment, Circuit Training - (HIIT IT HARDER DAY 5)
description:
DAY 5 HIIT IT HARDER CHALLENGE: 40 min Killer HIIT Workout!! Get pumped up - we're working the FULL BODY, burning calories and having fun because it's FRIDAY! Grab your mat, let's do it!!

WORKOUT DETAILS
0:00 Warm Up: 5 MIN 
5:15 Circuit Style Training 30 MIN = 50 Sec Work, 10 Sec Rest
35:15 Cool-Down: 5 MIN

🏋🏼‍♀️ Equipment: No

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your OWN workout... take a longer break when you need to.
